      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the \"different sides\" thing, but you're being kinda vague. like, can't we look at the actual impact? for example, when people use these ideas to call out stuff or change policies, isn't that objectively progress, or is the \"censorship\" argument actually a valid critique of how it's being handled?",
