      "content": "but you said the \"censorship\" argument is valid... which feels like you're giving a lot of weight to critics who just want to maintain the status quo. if the goal is fixing systemic injustice, isn't \"policing language\" just a necessary part of breaking down old power structures? it seems like calling it \"censorship\" is just a way to delegitimize the actual fight for equality.",
